title: GORGEOUS VIEW FURNISHED IN ICON South of Fifth!!!
posting_body: ['the exclusive ICON South Beach.', 'A true 3 bedroom, all with private bathrooms, large closets and water views.', 'One of the largest floor plans in the building with floor to Ceilling windows and ample entertainment space including oversized wrap around balcony.', 'Highly desirable unit with ocean to bay view from from 16th floor that provides picturesque sunrise and sunsets.', 'Hotel like amenities with everything at your fingertips from concierge services, valet, on site restaurant, 2 pools and state of the art fitness center.pet friendly, additional parking available.', 'Unit was completely renovated and furnished', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
